response.overview: Medal is a story of an ambitious boxer whose life revolve in a dilemma to give priority to expenses of his high protein diet or his household expenses. His responsibilities for his family avert him from boxing but on the ontherside his ambition to earn a gold medal make him fight for that again and again. But at last even after winning world championship he was provided with a gold plated medal which was prove to be useless during his hard time - this is all about "Medal - pet nahi Bharta"
response.title: Medal Pet Nahi Bharta
